name: Naturals' Man T-Shirt
description:
Our first t-shirt especially for men that love Natural Hair.

Front: I Love It Nappy. Not Fake. Not Straight.

Back: I'm A Naturals' Man

Screen Color: Black

T-Shirt Fabric: 5-ounce, 100% cotton jersey (preshrunk), Double-needle sleeves and hem, Double-needle cover stitching on front neck.

Sizes: Small, Medium, Large, X-Large, 2X-Large, 3X-Large

Colors: White, Sports Grey, Tennessee Orange, Natural, Red, Sage, Sky Blue, Burnt (Bright) Orange, Aquatic Blue, Lime Green. 

If you would like a color other than White, please remember to include your color choice in notes.
